{"type":"article","id":19084,"title":"招商银行调研：4月份小微企业产能仅恢复4成","uid":176,"topics":[26],"contents":"招商银行小微企业调研报告：<br>\n4月末我国小微企业（雇员人数小于50）产能仅恢复四成，大中企业（雇员人数超过100）产能恢复约七成。受产能恢复缓慢影响，小微企业对未来的预期也更为悲观。<br>\n令人担忧的是，除湖北外，对复工前景最悲观的是我国经济最发达的地区：北京、广东、上海。<br>\n<br>\n——利维坦正在步履蹒跚<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wNlFb9j.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wNlFb9j.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wNlFb9j.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/zK0nQD4.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zK0nQD4.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/zK0nQD4.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/PL86sW1.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PL86sW1.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/PL86sW1.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-05-20","agreeCount":7,"discussionCount":0}